text:
One, Two, Three, then
turn, and ta-tan, right...?

Wasn't it: One, Two, Three,
then ta-tan, tataan?

The two of you
are working hard, huh.

Shall we review a video 
of the choreography together?

We're trying our best!
Anyway, which of us was right, Producer?

Umm... Let's check the choerography
video to confirm that.

Wah...
That sounds good...! Thank you.
